    <a href="http://e2enetworks.com/">E2E Networks</a>.
  {%- else %}
    Hasjob is a service of <a href="https://hasgeek.com/">HasGeek</a>.
    Subscribe to <a href="{{ url_for('feed') }}">the feed</a> or follow
